#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1822
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Consult the <ulink url=\"man:terminfo(5)\">terminfo</ulink> or <ulink url="
"\"man:termcap(5)\">termcap</ulink> database for the expected escape "
"sequences and control characters that each key combination is supposed to "
"send."
